FOR OVER 60 YEARS ACTRESS ON STAGE, FILM AND TV

[UNDER SEAT]
BELOVED WIFE OF FELIX BROWN, MOTHER, GRANDMOTHER AND FRIEND"ż
ĪIn loving memory of Jean Fennell (June 1951- April 2011)
actor and beloved teacher who nurtured and inspired
her actors with the teachings of Sandford Meisner."ż
ĪIn memory of Richard Dodds
30 August 1965 - 27 October 2015
together with Violet Danvers, Dame Agatha Garnett and Matron
With love from his family and friends"”
ŻLydia Charlotte Bate
19 Sep 1982 to 25 Dec 2006
With grateful thanks to the staff of
Rahere Ward, St Bartholomew's Hospital 2
for outstanding care and kindness"¦
